        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure3C shows immuno-gold localisation of betaIII spectrin, the gold particles accumulate at the spine neck and dendrite. Gold particles are never observed in proximity of the PSD, their average distance to the postsynaptic membrane is 416±260 nm (p6448).. Experimental description: Figure legend: \"C, Immunogold EM of III spectrin staining in thin sections of mouse brain. \"" ;
